item.title: [HBASE-16152] HBase1.1.2 jmx some table region information missing
item.description: When opened ip::16030/jmx , i found that some table region information is missed in "Hadoop:service=HBase,name=RegionServer,sub=Regions"。
item.summary: HBase1.1.2 jmx some table region information missing

status.description: The issue is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.

here is one table situation.

i can saw the table "anycall" in table table.jsp .
